{
  "stem": "11771.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the old synagogue, what I find there in the same scenery like in about five, six people-- it was a smaller synagogue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they brought there, also, same people from a neighboring village, [NON-ENGLISH], but they were locked up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the time they were insane, not normal people they brought in in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When one of them-- when they trapped me in with a kick, inside the door, and they accept me with laughter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- surrounding me, it was there normal people from Ejszyszki, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can recognize them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But most of them they brought from all kind of institutions-- the insane people, the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When one picked me up, a 2 meter guy, a tall guy he picked me up like a fly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was a small guy, a skinny guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When he put me in it was an [NON-ENGLISH], it was like a bow hanging on the wall towards the end in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When he put me in the bow, when everybody laughs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When he started was there, [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH] were in the synagogue from people, and they start to beat me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I was fainting from pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then eventually one stood up and saved me from them, a Jew from inside who took me out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When I told him the story, exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was laying there with scratches on my-- on my body, till I got rid of them, after the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then after they took me out, it's they threw in the Lithuanian, they threw in another guy there, who got caught.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was like-- like a punish place to pick up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I asked him, put me in the other synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They knew where my father is.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
